title: Central Statistics Office Ireland, Population Statistics by Town, Ireland, 2002 & 2006
name: Central Statistics Office Ireland, Population Statistics by Town, Ireland, 2002 & 2006
description: This dataset has population figures for Ireland by Selected Towns for the Years 2002 and 2006. The towns have been placed by their lat/lon through geocoding processes. These population figures include total population 2002 and 2006, male population 2006, and female population 2006. Also the difference between the two years total figures are available as well as the percentage change. The data comes from Central Statistics Ireland. for more info go to: cso.ie.
